.DT
set_pawn_ttl
Disk World creator help
set_pawn_ttl

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_pawn_ttl -  This sets the time to live of pawned items, in seconds.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_pawn_ttl(int ttl)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ttl%^RESET%^ - The time in seconds before the shop will sell a pawned item.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/pawn_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets the time to live of pawned items, in seconds.  That is, the
length of time between an item being pawned and the shop selling that
item to recoup its costs.  The default is one week realtime.
.EP

